        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">PIXEL places X between vowels:</span> The I-X-E pattern in PIXEL makes it easy to connect to existing words on the board. Look for spots where I or E are already placed and build PIXEL across them.</p></div>
